comments: Hunter (ATL) brings his hands towards Lillard's (POR) front and marginal contact occurs as Lillard gathers the ball to pass.
Capela (ATL) is already in Hart's (POR) path and he absorbs the contact during the pick.
Hart (POR) makes contact with the part of Murray's (ATL) hand that is not on the ball, and the contact affects his jump shot.
Eubanks (POR) brings his hand toward Murray (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as Eubanks releases away to roll.
Capela (ATL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hunter (ATL) legally contests Simons' (POR) jump shot attempt.
Capela's (ATL) left hand briefly grasps Eubanks' (POR) right arm and marginal contact occurs as Eubanks' right hand simultaneously deflects the ball away from Eubanks.
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Murray's (ATL) arm as he is starting his upward shooting motion, and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Eubanks (POR) is already in Murray's (ATL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.

Replay review of the foul called on Lillard (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Lillard (POR) makes contact with Murray's (ATL) right hand as he is gathering the ball, and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) is already in Payton II's (POR) path and does not deliver contact during the dribble hand-off.
Capela (ATL) brings his hands toward Lillard (POR) and marginal contact occurs as Capela releases away to roll.
Payton II (POR) makes contact with Bogdanovic's (ATL) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) steps into the lane prior to the release of Bogdanovic's (ATL) free throw attempt.
Eubanks (POR) brings his hands towards Collins (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as Collins' momentum carries him away from the rebound.
Hunter (ATL) wraps Lillard (POR) prior to making any contact with the ball.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Grant (POR).
Capela (ATL) is already in Payton II's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Payton II (POR) places his hand momentarily on Murray's (ATL) hip and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Hart (POR).
Capela (ATL) and Eubanks (POR) briefly engage and disengage as they position themselves for a potential rebound.
Portland signals for a timeout, and the timeout is awarded prior to the ball being deflected out of bounds.
Murray (ATL) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
